race.description: Boxing Day Tickets On Sale Now Mdn Plate
race.comment: CHICAGO KING (1) holding his form and surely today is the day he gets off the mark at start thirteen. Closed off strongly last start to finish third over 1350m at Ipswich. Will be tough to stop again with a more positive ride. TAGA SMILE (10) improving filly coming along nicely at her second prep. Came out positive from the low draw and held on gamely when second over 1400m at the Sunshine Coast. Can take control and prove hard to run down. INQUISITOR (6) heavily supported for the new yard ($1.80 fav), when he gripped on late to secure second over 1200m at the Gold Coast Poly. Near his top and has genuine top three claims. STRENUOUS (7) beaten for early speed on resumption when a plugging fourth over 1206m at Grafton. Comes to hand quickly and looking for the 1400m now.
